---
title: Berbere-Spiced Salmon with Summer Vegetable and Orzo Salad
description: Berbere is an Ethiopian spice blend with garlic, red pepper, cardamom, coriander, and fenugreek. Although it’s traditionally found in soups and stews, our chefs had a feeling the warm and smoky flavors would work well with salmon, and we couldn’t agree more.
